metadata.name: Dive in
metadata.description:
Dive in is a 1 (of 1) of a 3-part collection 'Forest Yellows'.

Mike has worked as a circus performer for the last 10 years, throughout this time he has developed a passion for Web3 and become very interested in how he can try to replicate the magic of the circus in a digital landscape. 

This collection was conceptualized, captured, and performed all by Mike, to see the process a full behind-the-scenes video of the photoshoot will be released on 01/07/2022.

'Forest Yellows' is Mike's first NFT collection - Exploring the connections between humans, nature, and the unusual. 

This project is made up of 3 unique 1 of 1 photographs.
